# General Guidelines
- Maintain decoupled architecture (Backend/Frontend).
- Clean, modular code.

# Backend (FastAPI)
- Best practices for FastAPI + SQLite.
- Pydantic V2 strictly: use `pattern=r"..."` (not regex), and use `model_config = ConfigDict(...)` (not class Config).
- Keep dependencies updated but adhere to fixed requirements when dictated.

# Frontend (Svelte + Tailwind V4 + DaisyUI)
- Strictly use Tailwind V4 syntax.
- `app.css` should only use `@import "tailwindcss";` and `@plugin "daisyui";`.
- Use the `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin in `vite.config.js`. DO NOT use old Tailwind V3 syntax.
- Center main app elements with Flexbox/Grid centering (`min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-base-200`).
